snippet.title: Dreadhunter - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1553710/Dreadhunter/

Drop into action inside a cutting edge mech suit. Shoot, slash, smash and dash to get to the highest bounties as a fearless sci-fi monster hunter.
